714444f-a.text:

P. L. Sperr.

707658f-a.title: Manhattan: 1st Ave. - 75th St. E.
707658f-a.text:

Buildings concerned are 3-story frame houses. Also shown is East 75th
Street, at, adjoining and west of the S.W. corner of First Ave.
September 25, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
